eb81337e","tid":2382240,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"之前唔係已經話會撤出中國咩"},{"pid":"ae14f75856ed3300613fc858170aba4556c7a473","tid":2382240,"uid":10056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"乜鳩野消然"},{"pid":"27b94b98bde14db011ab032a81a1e41d74be30a5","tid":2382240,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/01/25/a103039837.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2021%2F01%2F25%2Fa103039837.html&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdnz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=cd8db3d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/01/25/a103039837.html</a>"},{"pid":"4e28f48756c43c6418880e8137fd1efc761c52e2","tid":2382240,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1f3655665a0f71a5981c07c859376f6e533bc5b","tid":2382240,"uid":98317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"IBM唔係It公司咩，關電機咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:35:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/01/25/a103039837.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2021%2F01%2F25%2Fa103039837.html&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdnz632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=cd8db3d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/01/25/a103039837.html</a>"},{"pid":"d6588162eb13838de02b30ed4e8845e611dc5145","tid":2382240,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:37:05.000Z","msg":"IBM中國研究所研發物聯網雲計算<br />\nIBM中國研究院成立於1995年9月，位於北京中關村，它是IBM全球12大研究機構之一。2008年，IBM中國研究院上海分院成立。IBM中國研究院主要從事物聯網雲計算、雲計算基礎設施與雲服務、平台即服務（PaaS）的開發與研究。<br />\n據介紹，二十多年來，該研究院曾有過上千名研究人員，其中絕大多數擁有中國乃至世界一流大學的碩士或博士學位。據報道，許多知名的科技成果都出自該研究院，包括著名的人工智能程序「沃森」。"},{"pid":"151adf4888c82eb8b306da427490db2f558d98c8","tid":2382240,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f86a77b0ebcc289d66edaa23e4ddc1d9a65bb688","tid":2382240,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:00:11.000Z","msg":"國際電機巨頭IBM 中國研究院消然關閉，遷往印度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j9x8nPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj9x8nPC.jpg&h=2139eb45&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"澄清：美國IBM中國研究院（IBM CRL）近期關閉。該機構為IBM全球12大研究機構之一。另外，國際電機巨頭德亨電機宣布將2條生產線搬遷至印度。"}]}